	.about
		.container
			.row.about_content#about
				.col-md-6

					.div.line

					h1
						| About
						br
						| Ominira

					p.
						Ominira escrow protocol allows users to exchange
						different crypto, digital and fiat currencies fast 
						and secure platform. It reduces the risk of fraud by
						acting as a third party who recieves and disburse
						funds to both buyer and seller based on set agreements.

				.col-md-6.escrow
