			.row

				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/6.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Agreement
								span Buyer and seller agrees to terms. Either the buyer or the seller begins a transaction.

				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/2.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Tokens Purchase
								span The buyer purchases Ominira tokens for fiat currency, and deposits the OEN in an escrow account by using an OTP generated through e-mail, or on the users phone.

				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/3.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Buyer pays Ominiraprotocol.io
								span The buyer submits a payment. Ominiraprotocol.io verifies the payment, and then notify the seller that funds have been secured in Escrow.

				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/7.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Seller sends the currency
								span Upon payment verification, the seller is authorised to send the coin/token and submit proof of information. Ominiraprotocol.io verifies that the buyer receives.
				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/4.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Buyer accepts
								span The buyer has a set number of minutes as per the terms to verify the token/coin and the option to accept or reject it.

				.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.box
						.row
							.col-sm-12
								img(src="./img/5.jpg" alt="agreement icon").responsive-image.center
								
								span.head_text
									strong Ominiraprotocol.io pays the seller
								span Ominiraprotocol.io releases funds to the seller from the escrow account

